item.description: SoftLayer_Container_Network_ContentDelivery_Authentication_Directory Datatype Description SoftLayer_Container_Network_ContentDelivery_Authentication_Directory represents a token authentication directory on your CDN FTP or on your origin server. Local createDate The date that a token authentication directory was created. Type: dateTime name The name of a directory or a file within a directory listing. Type: string type The type of platform that a token authentication directory is defined for.
